### Upload PDF → PDF/A (default: version 2b)
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/pdf-to-pdfa
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../fixtures/sample.pdf
--boundary--

### Upload PDF → PDF/A-1b
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/pdf-to-pdfa?pdfa_version=1b
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../fixtures/sample.pdf
--boundary--

### Upload PDF → PDF/A-3b
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/pdf-to-pdfa?pdfa_version=3b
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../fixtures/sample.pdf
--boundary--

### Poll task status
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}

### Download result
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}/download
